questions.title: Majority Element II
questions.description: Given an integer array of size n, find all elements that appear more than ⌊ n/3 ⌋ times.

questions.title: Spiral Matrix II
questions.description: Given a positive integer n, generate an n x n matrix filled with elements from 1 to n^2 in spiral order.

questions.title: Extra Characters in a String
questions.description: You are given a 0-indexed string s and a dictionary of words dictionary. You have to break s into one or more non-overlapping substrings such that each substring is present in dictionary. There may be some extra characters in s which are not present in any of the substrings. Return the minimum number of extra characters left over if you break up s optimally.
